The Municipal Treasurer informed the team that the Bureau of Local Government Finance (BLGF) computes the target for each LGU based on the following criteria:
80% of the current collection;
30%= delinquent for the past for (4) years. The total of the above will be the amount to be set-up at the beginning of the year.  According to management, this is the most realistic approach as affirmed by the BLGF because land ownership has many issues such as idle or contested lot; unknown owners, etc.

